{"tid":262515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潛宿舍偷學長利是錢以還卡數     城大三年級生囚34個月","createTime":"2017-05-29T09:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T10:11:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21f42467bf0c53da1e9c5ef7d4872b268bfee9de","tid":262515,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496050891_41c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496050891_41c2.jpg&h=2998e874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n城大中文系三年級男生去年4月多次潛入宿舍多間房間，先後偷取學長6,700元及女生100元，之後再次潛入學長宿舍匿藏在廁所，準備再下手時被學長發現。男生早前承認入屋犯法及企圖入屋犯法等3罪，今被判入獄1年10個月。一直獲保釋兼已完成畢業試的被告聞判後哭成淚人。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指，已考慮被告曾俊言(25歲)為人努力，體育方面有好成續，又表明願意還錢，亦主動承認犯案且涉款不多。<br />\n被告早前求情透露因欠下信用卡數而犯案，及後再解釋指被告在內地的姨姨患癌，被告母親幫忙付醫藥費，被告在案發前以信用卡提取4萬元幫忙，加上手續費及遲還錢罰款，債項累積，被告才被逼犯案。"},{"pid":"083fb29ec8b39bb7be70a27a28b696fc95329ff2","tid":262515,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"身為天之驕子使唔使偷錢呀"},{"pid":"338c8705f235a40ba4960bdcfaea1bb64dc97860","tid":262515,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"被大６婆呃定自己都係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04106b50a19d570deea86471d8edd7364173be14","tid":262515,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被大６婆呃定自己都係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講佢賭得好犀利"},{"pid":"c9b567f1e4d9779ef143889c80df8c7fc1e264c4","tid":262515,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"未畢業信用卡拎到4萬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf290ab15003d563c06b4566ec8dc8b0cb04ed","tid":262515,"uid":38143,"like"